				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "A frightened bystander on the ground floor of Moonrise Tower. He's deeply upset by the scrying eyes wandering the tower. He's caught between religious rapture and terror - he dreads and loves the Absolute in equal measure."
